### ✅ Register Jobseeker
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/jobseeker/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aarav Mehta",
  "email": "aarav.mehta@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass456!",
  "mobile": "+918888777666",
  "workStatus": "open to offers",
  "experience": {
    "years": 4,
    "months": 3
  }
}

###

### ✅ Login as Jobseeker
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "aarav.mehta@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass456!",
  "userType": "jobseeker"
}

